description:
An open profile where an activity can always be created because they are restricted to a single word with a single word name.

A "tag" as a single word means that no matter what tag someone creates anyone can use that tag as well. Normally an Activity is only shared when it will have the same meaning to everyone, as a single word (English or not) a tag naturally has the same meaning.

To create an Activity under this profile simply use the format: `http://id.tincanapi.com/activity/tags/<your word>`. Then use the same word in the Activity Definition 'name' property with the 'und' (undefined) language map code for the language. The corresponding Activity looks like this:

```json
{
    "id": "http://id.tincanapi.com/activity/tags/<your word>",
    "definition": {
        "name": {
            "und": "<your word>"
        }
    },
    "objectType": "Activity"
}
```
